data.description: Welcome home to your countryside estate on 2.57 acres in Dorchester County on Maryland’s Eastern Shore. This beautiful 2,400+ square foot home includes four full bedrooms, two and one-half bathrooms, spacious living, family and dining rooms along with an eat-in kitchen, laundry room and spacious back deck. The 4 Bay Garage is the ultimate with ample room for office/cars/workshop. Additional highlights include a brand-new paved driveway back to the garage, all new stainless steel appliances, hook-up for electric cars, brand new first floor HVAC, fresh paint and many more. PRICE IMPROVEMENT 10/23 ... MOTIVATED SELLER!!
